author: fdmanana
msg: Micro optimization: when reading an iolist, read up to 8Kbs instead of the 4 bytes length prefix only in the first file read operation.
For reads of small terms/iolist (up to 8Kbs), this speeds up the whole operation. No impact on larger terms/iolists.
